data.description: This townhome, located in the desired Canyon Lakes at Stone Gate, is ideal for a starter home or investment property. Built in 2004 and updated in 2019 with brand new stainless appliances and hardwood flooring, the interior is pleasing. Downstairs features kitchen/ dinning area with island, living area and a half bath. Upstairs features two bedrooms, both with ensuite bathrooms, balcony and laundry room. The home has a small yard, with enough space to play with kids or pet or entertain a small group of friends. Located a minutes drive from dining, shopping and entertainment in Town Lake and a walking distance to community features such as tennis court, splash pad, parks and a golf course. Students are zoned to Cy-Fair ISD. Efficiency, comfort and style makes this property a must see in the area. Have your agent schedule a showing. If you are unrepresented, contact listing agent for more information.
